sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Controller
    participant AWS as AWS EC2
    participant N as Node
    participant A as Agent

    C->>AWS: RunInstances
    AWS-->>C: instance-id + pending
    Note over C: node row: PROVISIONING

    loop every 5s
        C->>AWS: DescribeInstances
    end
    AWS-->>C: running
    Note over C: PROVISIONED

    AWS-->>N: (instance boots)
    N->>C: Vector: cloud-init logs (WebSocket)
    Note over C: CONFIGURING → CONFIGURED

    C->>N: SSH: scp agent, write config,<br/>enable systemd unit
    Note over C: DEPLOYING → DEPLOYED

    N->>A: systemd starts agent
    A->>C: WebSocket open + Register
    Note over C: REGISTERING → REGISTERED
    A->>C: Heartbeat
    Note over C: ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT<br/>materialize returns outputs
